1Ô∏è‚É£2Ô∏è‚É£ Debian Boot Process ‚Äî Full Deep Flow

Now the most important part you asked:

BIOS ‚Üí Kernel loading ‚Üí OS startup

Let‚Äôs go step-by-step.

‚∏ª

üß≠ Boot Overview

Power ON
   ‚Üì
BIOS / UEFI
   ‚Üì
Bootloader (GRUB)
   ‚Üì
Kernel loads
   ‚Üì
